{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_yw9xpyk6dn3l5lb10r9i9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"336985787","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/claude-code/2026-07-21T17-57-52-415Z/baseline-docs-from-code-2/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","content":"# Cache API\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a new in-memory cache instance that provides key-value storage functionality.\n\n```javascript\nimport { createCache } from './cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\nReturns an object with the following methods for cache operations.\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by its key.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The key to look up\n\n- **Returns:** The cached value associated with the key, or `undefined` if not found\n\n```javascript\ncache.get('myKey')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a value in the cache under the specified key.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The key to store the value under\n  - `value` - The value to store\n\n- **Returns:** The stored value\n\n```javascript\ncache.set('myKey', 'myValue')\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves a value from the cache by its key.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The key to delete\n\n- **Returns:** Boolean indicating whether a value was successfully deleted\n\n```javascript\ncache.delete('myKey')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```javascript\ncache.clear()\n```\n"}}],"model":"qwen/qwen3.5-9b","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4769,"output_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":4669},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"303b360e-afe6-44d9-bbbc-7f828d7bb7d6","uuid":"21c76fb3-e3c0-4273-963d-8cdecd0d7daa","timestamp":"2026-07-21T23:31:11.532Z"}
